The Bucks' victory serves as a reminder that success is achievable even in challenging circumstances.

name: Dennis Rodman
summary: Trinity Rodman, an Olympic gold medalist and soccer star daughter of NBA legend Dennis Rodman, has publicly denounced her father's role in her life. In a series of interviews and statements, Rodman expressed her strained relationship with her father, claiming that his absence and partying lifestyle have left her feeling traumatized. She emphasized that while he may be her biological father, he has not acted as a responsible parent and does not deserve the title of "dad." Rodman's comments have sparked discussions about the impact of absent or neglectful parents on their children, as well as the complexities of family dynamics.

summary: Multiple news sources have reported on the findings of a watchdog investigation into the FBI's role before the January 6th Capitol riot. name: Government shutdown
summary: The United States Congress is currently debating a funding bill that would provide over $100 billion in disaster aid. The bill has bipartisan support, but President Trump opposes it and has urged Republican lawmakers to reject it. As a result, the government is at risk of a shutdown on December 20, 2019. In an effort to avert a shutdown, Congress has enacted a Continuing Resolution that will keep the government funded through December 20, 2024. However, this is only a temporary solution, and Congress will need to reach an agreement on a long-term funding bill before that date.

name: Recalled Potato Chips
summary: Frito-Lay has announced a limited recall of Lay's Classic Potato Chips distributed in Oregon and Washington due to undeclared milk, a known allergen. The affected products have been recalled as they pose a potential health risk to individuals with milk allergies or sensitivities. The recall is specific to a limited number of chip bags, and the affected states are clearly listed in the news reports. Consumers in the impacted areas are advised to check the labels of their Lay's Classic Potato Chips and refrain from consuming any products that are part of the recall. Frito-Lay has urged customers to contact their consumer relations team with any questions or concerns regarding the recall.

name: Liz Cheney
summary: House Republicans, led by Chairman Loudermilk, have released a second report on the January 6, 2021, attack on the U.S. Capitol, making accusations against Congresswoman Liz Cheney and calling for her investigation. The report alleges that Cheney interfered with witnesses in the January 6 committee's work, and some Republicans, including former President Trump, have expressed support for the accusations. Trump has urged the FBI to probe Cheney, and the GOP report recommends a criminal investigation. These developments have sparked controversy and raise questions about the motivations behind the investigation and its potential impact on Cheney's work on the January 6 committee.
